thread.title: Sam Venning
thread.title_full: Ink Station reviewed by Sam Venning

author: Sam Venning
title: Sam Venning
text: Inkstation.com.au provides me with consumables (toner every few months and less frequently drum unit) for a couple of home laser printers. Inkstation web site is easy to navigate, stock availability consistently good, prompt delivery and top pricing. Excellent service by any measure. I will continue using Inkstation to source printer consumables.
